msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt_touzoku04_Finish"
msgid ""
"\"Armor worn by fierce phantoms, feared even by\n"
"heroes, is hidden in the ruins of Hyrule Field.\n"
"Find these pieces at a battleground where brave\n"
"souls tested their skill...at ceremonial grounds\n"
"where royal guards are honored...and at the\n"
"ruins where the soldiers of Hyrule gathered.\"\n"
"\n"
"You found the treasure that was hidden at\n"
"Coliseum Ruins, Sacred Ground Ruins,\n"
"and Hyrule Garrison Ruins. You obtained\n"
"the <1.se_co>Phantom Equipment<2.re_co>!"
msgstr ""

